		  <td width="3"></td>
          <td class="mainbody">
<p>
If a powerful magical blasting is your thing, you must be a wizard. And as a wizard, you shy away from those papers that burn up too easily. What you want is the fire retardant runes. The fact that others think they are just pretty rocks is a tricky way to get them cheap. Don't enlighten the poor deluded souls who just hand them too you, otherwise they might be tossed at you ... hard.
</p><br><div align="right">Last Modified By: EQTC Editor Krazick&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>

		Last Modified on: 2003-07-09 11:24:13&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</i></div><br>
